    ServerPackCreatorAddon
    A ServerPackCreator addon provides additional functionality to ServerPackCreator via any of ConfigCheckExtension PostGenExtension PreGenExtension PreZipExtension ConfigPanelExtension TabExtension and ExtensionConfigPanel ExtensionTab

Package de.griefed.serverpackcreator.addons Description

Annotations for ServerPackCreator plugins/addons. If you plan on adding additional entrypoints for addons and/or plugins, make sure to extend from BaseInformation and put your new annotation into a sub-package corresponding to the part of ServerPackCreator where it will hook into.
